OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow a headteacher saved his
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpupils from a knifeman     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A knifeman who put a school into       
OL,6, lockdown for nearly two hours has been 
OL,7, detained indefinitely in a secure      
OL,8, psychiatric hospital.                  
OL,10,FMatthew Lennox entered St Joseph's     
OL,11,FCatholic High School, in Slough, on 27 
OL,12,FMarch last year, with a large knife    
OL,13,Ftucked into his waistband and telling  
OL,14,Fstaff he had a gun. One year later, the
OL,15,Fheadteacher who confronted him has     
OL,16,Fspoken out for the first time.         
OL,19,FUntil that moment it, had been a normal
OL,20,FMonday morning.                        
